cc:Work.dc:title: Old Sumo Wrestlers
cc:Work.dc:description: I think I totally forgot to upload this one! I hand coloured this one myself awhile ago, from an old black and white depiction of sumo wrestling. I tried to give it simple muted colours, so it would seem at home in it's era. In this picture you can see the sumo referee (on the left) and two wrestlers, behind them the small crowd of other wrestlers appreciates the show.
